Description: Traveler Guitar Speedster Travel Electric Guitar MINT CONDITION (Like-new condition). I purchased it new, put new strings on it, strummed a couples chords (to make sure it stayed in tune, which it did), then put it back in the box. I had planned on taking the guitar on a trip, but never needed it in the end. With its unique modern-retro look and detachable tear-drop arm support, the Speedster represents a design revolution in travel guitars. In addition to its compact size and portability, the Speedster is built for performance with a high-output dual-rail humbucker pickup, a unique roller-style bridge, and volume and tone controls. With the arm support detached for travel, the whole package fits neatly inside a high quality gig bag (included) and is small enough to stow in airline overhead compartments. The Traveler Speedster is great for the rocker on the run!FeaturesFull 24-3/4" scale 4 1/2 pounds light and only 28" long Fits easily in airline overhead compartments Dual-rail humbucker Volume and tone controls Upper armrest detaches for travel It retails new for $379.99.
